Get Home Court Arenas

Source: R/kp_misc_stats.R
kp_arenas.Rd

Get Home Court Arenas

kp_arenas(year = most_recent_mbb_season())

Arguments

year

Year of data to pull

Value

A data frame with 6 columns:

Rk

double.

Team

character.

Conf

character.

Arena

character.

Alternate

character.

Year

double.

Examples

# \donttest{
 try(kp_arenas(year=2021))
